2024-04-23 23:56:06 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1713916566,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"147.45.49.22","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (X11; Ubuntu; Linux x86_64; rv:114.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/114.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10002,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"4","project_id":"834","nick":"Josefina","topic":"I was on your website earlier","content":"Hi,\r\n\r\nIf I can tell you exactly which Businesses (B2B) visited your website today - would you be interested?\r\n\r\nHere is what I mean.\r\n\r\nYou get 100 visitors today.\r\n\r\n2 of them fill out your form.\r\n1 of them calls you.\r\n97 of them are gone forever... Until Now.\r\n\r\nOur software can track:\r\n\r\n    -Who was on your website\r\n    -How they got there\r\n    -What keyword they searched\r\n    -Their Name, Phone and Email address.\r\n\r\nDon't lose any more leads or sales opportunities.\r\n\r\nWe've been in business since 2015 with clients around the world.\r\n\r\nInterested? Send me your name and number for a no cost demo on YOUR website.\r\n\r\nLeadsMax.biz\r\n\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nWebsite Detective\r\nDon't Miss Any Opportunity.","create_date":"2024-04-23 23:56:06","modify_date":"2024-04-23 23:56:06","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2560559},"entity_changes":false}
